<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<body>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/foto-gratis/fondo-comunicacion-global-diseno-redes-empresariales_53876-160250.jpg'); /* Ruta de la imagen de fondo */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100vh;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .overlay {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Transparencia del fondo */
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            position: relative;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content {
            z-index: 2;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            padding-top:100px;
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</body>
<body>
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="content">
        <h1 class="display-3">Bienvenido a SoftTech</h1>
        <p class="lead">Descubre todo lo que tenemos para ofrecerte.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
